data.description: REDUCED, just in time to enjoy fall weather and football in this homes outdoor living spaces! Outdoor boasts a tv and fire pit under a wood pavilion, hot tub and a saltwater pool!  The 3br 3ba Ranch home has a large kitchen with eat in dining, a large den with gas fireplace and the updated master has a walk-in closet, en suite bath with a walk in shower and double quartz vanity. These sellers have made many updates and added a fenced in backyard and outliving space to enjoy year round, with a hot tub off the master and a beautiful in ground salt water pool and wood pavilion with tv and gas fire pit.
